    </p>
    
    <p>
      <br/>
      Account number: 38-9012-0815531-00 
      <br/>
      Name: Chalkle Limited
      <br/>
      Reference number: <%= @lesson.meetup_id %> - Your name
      <br/>
      Payment Amount: $<%= (@lesson.cost.present? ? @lesson.cost : 0) *1.15 %> per person incl. GST 
